{"tid":537302,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇長期返通頂既師兄覺得身體差左?","createTime":"2018-01-22T14:41:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-25T00:55:40.000Z","uid":155883,"like":132,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"5a4cd2e5542002b7dc73b2d679d75dd188b0c84e","tid":537302,"uid":155883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T14:41:40.000Z","msg":"返通頂真係大都癲<br />\n日夜長期調轉<br />\n早小小返到屋企都2am<br />\n晏既有時6am先收工<br />\n返到屋企沖埋涼就等如正常人返工<br />\n返醒都黃昏, 又要準備返工<br />\n長期係咁覺我訓幾耐都補唔返<br />\n<br />\n好多人話通頂係傷肝<br />\n以前唔信<br />\n而家成日暈下暈下...<br />\n有冇巴打明白"},{"pid":"8fd8302885e4ac061e3cf8a5dd7b27478b7701de","tid":537302,"uid":8867,"like":4,"dislike":22,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T14:45:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5aca7ad08bda4fd8ac8c10b4faa4a3f7dc9d8e86","tid":537302,"uid":74546,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T14:49:39.000Z","msg":"我返輪更，但唔係長夜。返左一個禮拜通宵更都已經好辛苦，黎緊仲有一星期先有早返...<br />\n有時真係唔明d 人點頂長夜<br />\n<br />\n巴打邊行？利申返機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3da5689f7ac4db8e88c59fd78cf7aace28f18fdd","tid":537302,"uid":127347,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T14:51:07.000Z","msg":"以前18，19歲果陣返通宵真係無問題，放工仲好精神，依家12點都已經頂唔到"},{"pid":"03e4d00c8067acb81d6c553d925e10b52c113ec7","tid":537302,"uid":23445,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T14:52:59.000Z","msg":"冇<br />\n返完打個丁,沖涼訓教<br />\n但都係習慣唔到有光之下訓教"},{"pid":"c30137cc873d538979d174e221b4f28a1ef716be","tid":537302,"uid":155883,"like":78,"dislike":3,"score":75,"quote":{"pid":"5aca7ad08bda4fd8ac8c10b4faa4a3f7dc9d8e86","tid":537302,"uid":74546,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T14:49:39.000Z","msg":"我返輪更，但唔係長夜。返左一個禮拜通宵更都已經好辛苦，黎緊仲有一星期先有早返...<br />\n有時真係唔明d 人點頂長夜<br />\n<br />\n巴打邊行？利申返機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T14:55:23.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺一去到 1-2am 身體就好似開始叫你訓覺<br />\n但你意識到你唔可以訓, 而家仲要體力勞動<br />\n同身體講頂住<br />\n去到4am 就係高峰期, 因為正常人係呢段時間最好訓<br />\n但你仲做緊<br />\n反而, 去到6am 準備收工可以休息<br />\n不過你突然覺得唔再眼訓<br />\n因為, 你過往都係around呢段時間起身做野...<br />\n唉..."},{"pid":"914dfa2b5b4aeb01247d90bd271ddb05d6f6e525","tid":537302,"uid":23416,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T14:59:35.000Z","msg":"有咩通宵pt介紹"},{"pid":"5a4efa97a8b61a9af2a072fcf36a8fff8654c06c","tid":537302,"uid":29802,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T15:00:07.000Z","msg":"12點1點係屋企都覺得眼訓啦  何況番通頂"},{"pid":"de18a57087157cad918369e8b83f1d42f6b01831","tid":537302,"uid":1255,"like":2,"dislike":118,"score":-116,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T15:01:19.000Z","msg":"輪更就話想死<br />\n我之前番地盤番8AM-8AM 24個鐘都未死<br />\n仲要8AM放工去做GYM ROOM訓涼食野訓兩個鐘再操<br />\n第朝8AM輪回地獄"},{"pid":"fddecafc178c30242537aea57ebdffec7238fbc3","tid":537302,"uid":144466,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T15:02:21.000Z","msg":"google 褪黑激素<br />\n只要保持訓果時環境夠黑暗就無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申:個人經驗，臨起身開窗或者開燈再賴一陣床，令身體開始運作先起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f562470854216a97a2b60c6c529b17627c39e02","tid":537302,"uid":144466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T15:03:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>google 褪黑激素<br />\n只要保持訓果時環境夠黑暗就無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申:個人經驗，臨起身開窗或者開燈再賴一陣床，令身體開始運作先起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有就係生理時鐘，唔可以一時早一時夜<br />\n時間穩定，睡眠質素好就無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ca0694508475e723a2aa40ea7fdc2c072828396","tid":537302,"uid":164457,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T15:04:24.000Z","msg":"我覺得我仲柒左"},{"pid":"f71f28b94b82935cbcf5e10f8d38c08e779c49a5","tid":537302,"uid":33878,"like":4,"dislike":53,"score":-49,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T15:10:04.000Z","msg":"咁有無覺得柒右？"},{"pid":"235662dc298cae98cdc88ee8c5d3593918bcff33","tid":537302,"uid":16425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T15:18:06.000Z","msg":"無 不過成日唔夠訓同埋早訓就好易紮醒"},{"pid":"545a715b5f269c59a11f25465399c33af10cfde9","tid":537302,"uid":49232,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T16:13:22.000Z","msg":"我係返長夜<br />\n早排未讀返書嗰陣係冇嘢 <br />\n其實我只要係一個靜嘅環境吓就瞓到<br />\n但而家朝早要返學 <br />\n例如星期一朝早有九點堂 就要直落到放學先有得瞓<br />\n想快啲grad 撚咗佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n起初真係辛苦<br />\n而家可能習慣咗就覺得一日半日冇咩所謂了"},{"pid":"ac702c67fead2bdd5ed183f04e04b0ff5c3568b1","tid":537302,"uid":58319,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f71f28b94b82935cbcf5e10f8d38c08e779c49a5","tid":537302,"uid":33878,"like":4,"dislike":53,"score":-49,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T15:10:04.000Z","msg":"咁有無覺得柒右？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T16:15:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6216d66db35a90ecce46c3293529a2cd6b1fdf14","tid":537302,"uid":24227,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T16:34:10.000Z","msg":"我有排返咗個零星期長夜<br />\n反而訓得足精神幾好<br />\n<br />\n依家要早午晚更輪住返<br />\n每更相隔兩三個鐘<br />\n我應該就嚟死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94b13b9c9e93401b3d68a262ae3ad1525c52f5bb","tid":537302,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c30137cc873d538979d174e221b4f28a1ef716be","tid":537302,"uid":155883,"like":78,"dislike":3,"score":75,"quote":{"pid":"5aca7ad08bda4fd8ac8c10b4faa4a3f7dc9d8e86","tid":537302,"uid":74546,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T14:49:39.000Z","msg":"我返輪更，但唔係長夜。返左一個禮拜通宵更都已經好辛苦，黎緊仲有一星期先有早返...<br />\n有時真係唔明d 人點頂長夜<br />\n<br />\n巴打邊行？利申返機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T14:55:23.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺一去到 1-2am 身體就好似開始叫你訓覺<br />\n但你意識到你唔可以訓, 而家仲要體力勞動<br />\n同身體講頂住<br />\n去到4am 就係高峰期, 因為正常人係呢段時間最好訓<br />\n但你仲做緊<br />\n反而, 去到6am 準備收工可以休息<br />\n不過你突然覺得唔再眼訓<br />\n因為, 你過往都係around呢段時間起身做野...<br />\n唉..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T16:37:46.000Z","msg":"三四點仲要凍凍地<br />\n更加想訓"},{"pid":"1b161fe1ed71dfc08616a0945c8848a8768ee333","tid":537302,"uid":22150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5aca7ad08bda4fd8ac8c10b4faa4a3f7dc9d8e86","tid":537302,"uid":74546,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T14:49:39.000Z","msg":"我返輪更，但唔係長夜。返左一個禮拜通宵更都已經好辛苦，黎緊仲有一星期先有早返...<br />\n有時真係唔明d 人點頂長夜<br />\n<br />\n巴打邊行？利申返機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T17:11:23.000Z","msg":"我都係係機場番工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 通宵好辛苦 仲有9日捱"},{"pid":"bb26b2c789daab2118d58affee1682201f166d42","tid":537302,"uid":33424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T20:18:59.000Z","msg":"連續返完幾日夜後正常時間訓覺會失眠, 岩岩呢次4個鐘先訓著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打們有冇助眠藥推介?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d09c5bc30ab01e699b53cf7bfed2c801edc5a22","tid":537302,"uid":161709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fddecafc178c30242537aea57ebdffec7238fbc3","tid":537302,"uid":144466,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T15:02:21.000Z","msg":"google 褪黑激素<br />\n只要保持訓果時環境夠黑暗就無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申:個人經驗，臨起身開窗或者開燈再賴一陣床，令身體開始運作先起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T21:13:08.000Z","msg":"眼罩同厚窗簾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13f04f682632e215d626a54429ab3de25d707afd","tid":537302,"uid":161709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb26b2c789daab2118d58affee1682201f166d42","tid":537302,"uid":33424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T20:18:59.000Z","msg":"連續返完幾日夜後正常時間訓覺會失眠, 岩岩呢次4個鐘先訓著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打們有冇助眠藥推介?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T21:14:07.000Z","msg":"唔好食藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依賴咗之後唔食就仆街了"},{"pid":"ebd14ca8f32a4d7dde407a61c9f39a6c9966c785","tid":537302,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T21:20:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"669da4cf84a97bb93d78fbffe76127417f17a193","tid":537302,"uid":44427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T21:27:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef62476fda0390e4ea51dd7ba331181db583457f","tid":537302,"uid":68043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T21:39:47.000Z","msg":"收8點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0f112c33a1f3f1bc18d02b9d28877b47bba9d7b","tid":537302,"uid":126042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T22:33:37.000Z","msg":"Hi <br />\n你地做邊行<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e194649e84436883acaa500e3ca3a3928064cc8f","tid":537302,"uid":136665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T22:38:22.000Z","msg":"賣菜仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9120ca20378f7f67527404426db09d554874e4f7","tid":537302,"uid":37176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T22:43:14.000Z","msg":"Part time翻通宵 一時翻工一時翻學 搞到個生理時鐘亂曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 通完頂會頭痛<br />\n<br />\n利申: 仲未收工 我好眼瞓zzzzz"},{"pid":"43370e88f59f8b09aa991414e15d0c4c55b39b0c","tid":5