 />\n無咩精神就一定架喇   就算番工做完野有得恰陣  點都唔夠   <br />\n個陣就唔覺有咩病痛<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n不過建議你唔太等錢洗都盡早脫離呢d生活 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17d19c12a5796d9ab55ba6111b3b9e231421ef0e","tid":537302,"uid":45185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T23:06:21.000Z","msg":"紀律部隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81cc650a43e619a462aca68068b8dee748e3751a","tid":537302,"uid":39013,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T23:08:31.000Z","msg":"長期返身體可以適應<br />\n返shift就真係早死"},{"pid":"4fc3ff3d4040f0bc83f5524cef09b6026a3c41a1","tid":537302,"uid":2547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T23:18:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但仲有成村人考紀律部隊"},{"pid":"714f8b99c5b36c8ee7f548247f7e7a76c95b8014","tid":537302,"uid":67318,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T23:19:10.000Z","msg":"小弟都返左7年夜&hellip;<br />\n身體差只係初期，無記性就後期<br />\n<br />\n最怕就係日間瞓瞓唔著或瞓得好少時間<br />\n之後轉返早就覺得好攰<br />\n<br />\n除左以上之外，都少左同朋友去玩<br />\n同家人食飯都要早走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n放假又攰，做運動既心情同時間都無<br />\n如果返完夜轉早仲要假休一日真係人都巔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好處就係&hellip;用健康換金錢囉&hellip;返夜有津貼嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83284b7951b640af93ed6222ca2b64c952af9d8b","tid":537302,"uid":6111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T23:19:53.000Z","msg":"屌那星 早兩個禮拜公司有野搞開左兩個禮拜通宵<br />\n依家正常返但每晚訓教都極易醒同一晚醒幾次<br />\n以前我可以一教唔醒訓天光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b095aaa9